After the transfer payment is successful, click the + button in the lower right corner to send a screenshot of the order. The agent will send the tomato coin to your account as soon as possible.

After the transfer screenshot is sent, please wait patiently for the agent to recharge it for you. If the agent has not been recharged for a long time, please click on the recharge feedback in the lower right corner of the wallet interface to tell us that we want to deal with it as soon as possible.

If you encounter a transfer reminder that the receipt account is restricted and cannot transfer, please contact the agent to obtain the latest receipt account before making payment. Do not transfer to the historical receipt account, in order to avoid the loss of your funds received.
